# в”Ђв”Ђ Claude Code в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
# CLAUDE.md is tracked вЂ” it's the primary AI context file for the project.
# .claude/ contains local settings (API keys, permissions) вЂ” never shared.
# EXCEPTION: .claude/rules/ ships with the repo вЂ” it is auto-loaded by the
# .claude/rules/ contract (Anthropic memory docs). The /* form below lets the
# negation re-include the rules subdirectory; git cannot re-include children
# of a fully excluded parent.
.claude/*
!.claude/rules/
!.claude/settings.json

